name: Falcom Renne
description:
Dreambooth model for the character Renne from the Kiseki (Trails) game series from Nihon Falcom.

For better results, use the following positive and negative prompts as style:

  • Positive: masterpiece, best quality, extremely detailed CG, 8k wallpaper

  • Negative: lowres, bad anatomy, bad hands, text, error, missing fingers, extra digit, fewer digits, cropped, worst quality, low quality, normal quality, jpeg artifacts, signature, watermark, username, blurry, artist name, bad feet, disfigured

To improve colors use the Anything V3 VAE.

modelVersions.name: v3.0
modelVersions.description:
Trained using filewords with a custom set of images from official artworks.

Based on CS4, Hajimari, and Kuro illustrations.
